{"word":"G3928 - παρέρχομαι - parérchomai - par-er'-khom-ahee - Come","slug":"G3928","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρέρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>parérchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-er'-khom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - parerchomai</b> - <i>par-er'-khom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>; to <i>come near</i> or <i>aside</i>, that is, to <i>approach</i> (<i>arrive</i>), <i>go by</i> (or <i>away</i>), (figuratively) <i>perish</i> or <i>neglect</i>, (causatively) <i>avert:</i> - come (forth), go, pass (away, by, over), past, transgress."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1330\">G1330</a>, <a href=\"#/G1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3922\">G3922</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4334\">G4334</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905\">G4905</a>, <a href=\"#/G565\">G565</a>"}]}